data.title: 88 celebrities you might not know are Canadian
data.meta_description: A list of celebrities you might not realize are originally from Canada
data.text:
Associated Press

Celebrities from Canada

As are neighbors to the north prepare to celebrate Canada Day this weekend, we acknowledge Canada's contribution to the world of entertainment here in the United States as well.

Check out our list of 88 actors, musicians and comedians born in Canada.

-Mike Rose, cleveland.com
